text: Gabriela-Eugenia Rotiș-Nagy (born 12 November 1980) is an Austrian-Romanian handballer who plays as a left back for Hypo Niederösterreich. ==International honours== *Champions League: **Finalist: 2009 *Cup Winners' Cup: **Finalist: 2004 *Champions Trophy: **Finalist: 2004 *Junior World Championship: **Winner: 1999 *Junior Handball Championship: **Winner: 1998 ==References== Category:1980 births Category:Living people Category:People from Sfântu Gheorghe Category:Austrian female handball players Category:Romanian female handball players Category:Expatriate handball players Category:Romanian expatriate sportspeople in Austria Category:Austrian expatriate sportspeople in Denmark Category:Romanian expatriate sportspeople in Denmark Category:Austrian expatriate sportspeople in Hungary Category:Romanian expatriate sportspeople in Hungary Category:Naturalised citizens of Austria Category:Austrian people of Romanian descent
title: Gabriela Rotiș
